{"type": "article", "id": 23042, "title": "铝制刀具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-01T07:34:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110538oZ7zwthRbI5LHUiJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套铝制的刀叉餐具名为 dune（沙丘），它的手柄和叉勺是垂直关系，使得过度地段形成一条曲线，就像一个小的沙丘，很有质感。这种设计挑战了人们的惯有用法，但设计师解释这是一种实验风格，它更像手术室的临床工具，象征着烹饪时的无限可能。搭配铝的材质，使这套餐具拥有轻盈的特征和质感。<a href=\"http://www.andreaponti.com/projects/dune.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110536MoSF6Twn5HVvja1f.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110537ms6Xe3I9bkwEQZLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110537DgbfjtoBKvNPFsUd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105379Z5SgMHWLonit6C4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}